room_title: Escape room "Virogenix Lab" by Escape Room Vero Beach in Port St. Lucie
room_description: As a new hire at Virogenix Lab, you have been assigned to the Special Projects Division to help Dr. Bloodworth develop and test her new Viral Delivery System. She says, “It’s going to change the world.” What could possibly go wrong? Save yourselves and the good doctor before time runs out and the lab and all its contents are incinerated.
